        "three-fields": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Three-Field Architecture",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>The Three-Field Architecture</h2><p>An Intelligence Field is AI infused with your IP. It becomes a co-intelligence — a living system you, your team, and your clients can interact with. Every engagement builds toward activating your full field.</p><p><strong>Internal Field</strong> — Your IP vault and Fractal Twin. Everything you've written, said, taught, and built — organized, permanent, and queryable.</p><p><strong>Client-Facing Field</strong> — What your customers interact with. Intake flows, onboarding, protocol dialogues, product discovery — always-on guidance in your voice.</p><p><strong>Collective Data Field</strong> — Cross-client pattern recognition. The collective pulse: recurring patterns, common questions, seasonality, emotional arcs. This is the value multiplier.</p>",
